Steps to install Spark with Scala in CentOS-7

Scala Installation Steps


1. wget http://www.scala-lang.org/files/archive/scala-2.10.1.tgz

2. sudo gedit .bash_profile

 	 Add the below entry inside the file.

	      export PATH=$PATH:/home/training/scala/bin

	save and close the file

3. source .bash_profile

4. scala



Spark Installation Steps


1.  wget https://archive.apache.org/dist/spark/spark-1.6.0/spark-1.6.0-bin-cdh4.tgz
2.  sudo  gedit  .bash_profile 

      export PATH=$PATH:/home/training/spark/bin

    Save and close
    
3.  source .bash_profile
4. spark-shell






